Subject: Need help with our StealthAIC - no clue what it is called since the Netwrix takeover
Description:
Need assistance with our AIC to ensure our scans are incorporating into it
Will have attachment. Please do not send a KB as I have additional questions.
Solution_Comment__c:
StealthAUDIT (SA)					        11.5.0.265
StealthAUDIT Access Information Center (AIC)	11.5.0.137
Symptom:
Need assistance with our AIC to ensure our scans are incorporating into it
Will have attachment. Please do not send a KB as I have additional questions.

Cause:
The AIC query was taking longer than the web console was allowed to maintain an active connection for the user(s) to correctly display the needed details.

Resolution:
Adjusted the AuthSessionTimeout for AIC FROM: 20 (default is 15min)  TO: 90 min. 
REF: Netwrix Access Information Center 11.5 > Administrator Overview for StealthAUDlT > Additional Configuration Options for StealthAUDlT > Timeout Parameter for StealthAUDlT
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/AIC_11.5/page/Content/Access/InformationCenter/Admin/AdditionalConfig/Timeout_Parameter.htm
